`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
**Callback injection pattern** — This module demonstrates a recurring codebase pattern: instead of importing Rapier/ECS directly, functions accept callbacks (`getHeldCube`, `setCubePosition`). This makes the module:
1. **Testable without WASM** — tests pass simple lambdas instead of mocking Rapier
2. **Decoupled** — the same logic works whether cubes are tracked in Miniplex, Koota, or a plain Map
3. **Composable** — callers wire dependencies at the integration layer (GameScene/GameLoop)
